db.title: PAHG: The Database of Human Multi-gene Families
db.description: Curated human multi-gene families and their members.
db.basicInfo: PAHG compiles human multi-gene families, unifies family definitions, and links to literature and external resources.
db.hostInstitution: National Center for Bioinformatics, Quaid-i-Azam University, Islamabad, Pakistan
